        <header>
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the "Flu-Be-Gone Wellness Center," where health meets happiness!</p>
        </header>
        <hr>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to transform flu prevention into a delightful and accessible experience for our community. We believe that staying healthy should be a joyful journey, not a daunting task. With a warm and welcoming atmosphere, our goal is to make wellness a fun adventure where everyone can participate and smile along the way.</p>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section>
            <h2>Meet Our Founder</h2>
            <p>Our founder, Dr. Amelia Sunshine, is the driving force behind our clinic. She has dedicated her life to ensuring that the community never fears staying healthy. Driven by a childhood fear of flu shots, she created "Flu Buster," our lovable mascot and symbol of strength against the flu. Together, they lead our mission to spread happiness and wellness throughout the community.</p>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <p>Our team of dedicated professionals includes expert doctors, nurses, nutritionists, and wellness enthusiasts who are committed to your health and well-being. Dr. Amelia Sunshine, Dr. Marcus Wellness, and Dr. Olivia Harmony, among others, are here to guide you on your wellness journey. They bring their unique expertise and warm personalities to create a healthier, happier community.</p>
        </section>
        <hr>
        <section>
            <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
            <p>We actively participate in community events, partnerships, and outreach to promote health and wellness. At the "Flu-Be-Gone Wellness Center," we're more than just a clinic; we're a part of your community's journey to wellness. Join us in the fight against the flu and create a happier, healthier world with a smile!</p>
        </section>
